{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe8dee150b","title":"在政治局扩大会议期间的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":true,"dates":[{"id":"107fec78eb","index":1,"year":1966,"month":4,"day":25,"articleId":"fe8dee150b"},{"id":"ee77a19282","index":0,"year":1966,"month":4,"day":16,"articleId":"fe8dee150b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9c13415a5e","type":"title","text":"在政治局扩大会议期间的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fe8dee150b"},{"id":"1e55f7c5df","type":"paragraph","text":"中国会不会出修正主义当权派的问题，一是出，一是不出；一是早出，一是晚出。还是早出好；搞好了可能不出，在中国出修正主义是困难的。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fe8dee150b"},{"id":"f0e55b5ee5","type":"paragraph","text":"书记处也是分化的，彭、陆、杨、谭、罗等都当过书记处书记，是不断分化，合乎辩证法。有人怕得要死。不分化是主观愿望。中央有，各省也会有。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fe8dee150b"}],"page":{"id":"0ac701c085","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fe8dee150b","start":496,"end":496}}}},"__N_SSG":true}